# Tactical suite template (expected: 50 mate-in-2/3 positions)
#
# Format per line:
# <piece-placement> <side-to-move> <castling> <ep-square> bm <uci-move>[ <uci-move> ...]; id "optional-id";
#
# Example:
# 6k1/5ppp/8/8/8/5Q2/6PP/6K1 w - - bm f3a8; id "example-1";
#
# Notes:
# - Use UCI coordinate moves in bm values (for example: e2e4, g7g8q).
# - Multiple bm moves are supported.
# - Replace this file with your real 50-position suite.